, <a href="/web/20180712210030/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_HCPCS_CUI=C2368473&amp;fLockTerm=Functional+outcome+assessment+documented+as+positive+using+a+standardized+tool+and+a+care+plan+based+on+identified+deficiencies+on+the+date+of+functional+outcome+assessment%2c+is+documented">Functional outcome assessment documented as positive using a standardized tool and a care plan based on identified deficiencies on the date of functional outcome assessment, is documented</a>
